{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/kalo-benda-di-sekitar-kita-bisa-ngomong/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"The Flying Cow &#8211; Kalo Benda Di Sekitar Kita Bisa Ngomong","content":"<p>Bro sis yang suka baca komik, tahu The Flying Cow nggak? Nanti deh ya bahas itu. Sekarang <em>gini </em><em>deh,</em> pernah kebayang ngga kalo misalnya benda-benda mati di sekitar kita ternyata bisa bersuara, bergerak, dan beraktivitas layaknya manusia biasa? Waw bakal kayak gimana yah?! Jadi seru apa malah bikin serem?? Misal kamu lagi duduk nih. Terus tiba-tiba, kursi yang kamu dudukin itu protes karena kamu keberatan! Wah malu banget dong bro sis, ketahuan deh berat badan kita nambah 🙂</p>\n<p>Atau ketika kamu ngetik di keyboard laptop kantor. Tombol-tombol yang kamu teken pas ngetik, ternyata mengeluarkan suara sesuai dengan hurufnya masing-masing. Hihihi pasti lucu banget ya ketika mereka nyebut “A”, “B”, “C”, dan semua orang bisa tahu kita lagi ngetik apa.<br />\nNah kira-kira benda apalagi ya yang bakal jadi lucu atau malah menyeramkan ketika mereka bisa bertingkah dan punya perasaan seperti manusia?</p>\n<p><strong>Air mineral</strong></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_167\" style=\"width: 331px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-167\" data-attachment-id=\"167\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/kalo-benda-di-sekitar-kita-bisa-ngomong/attachment/flyingcow1/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/FlyingCow1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"321,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Air Mineral\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Air Mineral&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/FlyingCow1-300x300.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/FlyingCow1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-167\" src=\"http://blog.ciayo.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/FlyingCow1.jpg\" alt=\"Air Mineral\" width=\"321\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/FlyingCow1.jpg 321w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/FlyingCow1-280x280.jpg 280w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/FlyingCow1-300x300.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 321px) 100vw, 321px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-167\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Air Mineral</p></div>\n<p>Tubuh manusia sebagian besar terdiri dari cairan. Air minum tuh udah jadi kebutuhan dasar yang pasti kita butuhin setiap hari. Kalo ternyata air mineral yang kita minum bisa ngomong, apa kabar tuh? Berarti dia bakal menjadi bagian dari diri kita dong?? Hiiii</p>\n<p><strong>Ketapel</strong></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_168\" style=\"width: 331px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-168\" data-attachment-id=\"168\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/kalo-benda-di-sekitar-kita-bisa-ngomong/attachment/flyingcow2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/FlyingCow2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"321,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Batu dan Ketapel\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Batu dan Ketapel&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/FlyingCow2-300x300.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/FlyingCow2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-168\" src=\"http://blog.ciayo.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/FlyingCow2.jpg\" alt=\"Batu dan Ketapel\" width=\"321\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/FlyingCow2.jpg 321w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/FlyingCow2-280x280.jpg 280w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/FlyingCow2-300x300.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 321px) 100vw, 321px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-168\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Batu dan Ketapel</p></div>\n<p>Alat yang satu ini dulu emang hits banget di masyarakat kita. Selain gampang ngegunainnya, ketapel juga bisa jadi senjata yang cukup berbahaya loh! Tapi anak-anak biasanya menjadikan ketapel sebagai mainan yang asik buat ngisengin temen, atau malah buat nembak mangga di pohon tetangga (jangan ditiru ya bro sis). Nah kalo ketapel bisa ngomong, kira-kira dia bakal ngasih nasihat ngga ya gimana cara pakainya yang bener?</p>\n<p><strong>Dongkrak</strong></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_169\" style=\"width: 331px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-169\" data-attachment-id=\"169\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/kalo-benda-di-sekitar-kita-bisa-ngomong/attachment/flyingcow3/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/FlyingCow3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"321,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Dongkrak\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Dongkrak&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/FlyingCow3-300x300.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/FlyingCow3.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-169\" src=\"http://blog.ciayo.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/FlyingCow3.jpg\" alt=\"Dongkrak\" width=\"321\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/FlyingCow3.jpg 321w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/FlyingCow3-280x280.jpg 280w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/FlyingCow3-300x300.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 321px) 100vw, 321px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-169\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Dongkrak</p></div>\n<p>Benda apa yang biasanya dibawa di mobil untuk jaga-jaga kalo harus ganti ban? Yup, bener banget…Jawabannya dongkrak! Kalo diibaratkan manusia, dongkrak ni pastinya orang yang kuat banget! Macem Ade Rai gitu kali ya. Tapi, kalo dongkrak bisa ngomong kira-kira doi bakalan bantu mengangkat mobil atau malah berpose ala-ala binaragawan lagi ikut kontes?</p>\n<p><strong>Hiasan Magnet di Kulkas</strong></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_170\" style=\"width: 331px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-170\" data-attachment-id=\"170\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/kalo-benda-di-sekitar-kita-bisa-ngomong/attachment/flyingcow4/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/FlyingCow4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"321,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Tempelan Kulkas\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Tempelan Kulkas&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/FlyingCow4-300x300.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/FlyingCow4.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-170\" src=\"http://blog.ciayo.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/FlyingCow4.jpg\" alt=\"Tempelan Kulkas\" width=\"321\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/FlyingCow4.jpg 321w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/FlyingCow4-280x280.jpg 280w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/FlyingCow4-300x300.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 321px) 100vw, 321px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-170\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Tempelan Kulkas</p></div>\n<p>Hiasan magnet buat di kulkas biasanya didapet dari oleh-oleh temen atau saudara yang baru pulang liburan. Bayangin kalo hiasan magnet di kulkas itu bisa ngomong, wah yang pasti kulkas kamu bakalan rame deh bro sis! Masing-masing bakal membanggakan daerah asalnya dan mungkin dengan bahasanya sendiri-sendiri! Butuh hiasan kulkas yang bisa nerjemahin berarti tuh biar nyambung!</p>\n<p>Wah segitu aja udah ribet banget, gimana dengan benda-benda lainnya ya? Nah, cerita tentang benda-benda di sekitar kita yang bisa bertingkah seperti layaknya manusia bisa kalian baca di serial komik <a href=\"https://ciayo.com/comic/the-flying-cow\">The Flying Cow</a>. Buat bro sis yang suka komik komedi, yuk langsung aja cekidot!</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"e69067cf-a0f5-5eea-8de6-5a380784526a"}}}